            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Shree Maheshwari Vidyalaya is one of the best school in Burrabazar area. Maheshwari Vidyalaya is under the management of the Maheshwari Sabha Trust, Kolkata, West Bengal. The trust was created at the instance of the renowned industrialist & great philanthropist Late G.D.Birla and Sri Ranganath Bangur. The school provides a conducive learning environment and offers a well-rounded education to its students up to 12th class. This is a coeducation school. The faculty at Shree Maheshwari Vidyalaya is highly competent and dedicated. They are experienced in their respective fields and employ effective teaching methods to ensure student engagement and understanding. The teachers are approachable and supportive, creating a positive and nurturing atmosphere for learning. The school has good infrastructure and well-maintained classrooms. The facilities are up to date and cater to the needs of the students. Shree Maheshwari Vidyalaya encourages extracurricular activities, which play a crucial role in the holistic development of students. The school organizes various events, competitions, and sports activities, allowing students to showcase their talents and develop teamwork and leadership skills. Moreover, the management is efficient and proactive in addressing any concerns raised by parents or students. They prioritize the well-being and academic progress of the students, ensuring a safe and conducive learning environment. In conclusion, Shree Maheshwari Vidyalaya 4, Sovaram Bysack Street is a commendable school that focuses on academic excellence, holistic development, and student welfare. It is highly recommended for parents seeking quality education for their children in Kolkata, West Bengal",
